Pound

Move 1

6.00s Melee

The user pounds in the designated direction, damaging opposing Pokémon in the area of effect and decreasing their movement speed by 40% for 2s.

47% SpA + 28 x (Level - 1) + 520

Pound Upgrade Choices

Egg Bomb

9.00s Ranged

The user hurls an egg at the designated location that explodes, damaging opposing Pokémon in the area of effect and throwing them away from the center of impact for 0.8s. A maximum of 2 uses can be kept in reserve for this move, and there is a 2s cooldown between uses.

If the user learns both Soft-Boiled and Egg Bomb, the uses kept in reserve for Egg Bomb is added to Soft-Boiled's reserve pool; this reserve pool is shared between both moves. The base cooldown for both moves becomes 5s. The cooldown between using the same move remains at 2s.

41% SpA + 21 x (Level - 1) + 460

Decreases the movement speed of opposing Pokémon hit by 40% for 2s.

Helping Hand

9.00s Buff

The user increases the movement speed and basic attack speed of themself and nearby teammates by 30% for 4s. When buffed, the user's auto attacks also become boosted attacks.

Increases the auto attack damage of all teammates buffed by this move by 15% for 4s.

Heal Pulse

Move 2

10.00s Recovery

The user restores the HP of themself and a designated teammate every 0.5s over 2s.

40% SpA + 0 x (Level - 1) + 60

Heal Pulse Upgrade Choices

Soft-Boiled

12.00s Recovery

The user throws an egg to a designated teammate, restoring the HP of themself and the designated teammate. The user and the designated teammate restore HP over time every 1s over 2s afterward. Subsequent uses of this move overwrites any HP over time the user and the designated teammate is yet to restore from previous uses. A maximum of 2 uses can be kept in reserve for this move, and there is a 2s cooldown between uses.

170% SpA + 0 x (Level - 1) + 220

70% SpA + 0 x (Level - 1) + 85

Gains 1 additional use kept in reserve.

Safeguard

9.00s Buff

The user cleanses themself and a designated teammate, and grants the user and the teammate a shield that makes them unstoppable for 4s.

204.7% SpA + 15 x (Level - 1) + 690

Strengthens the value of the shield effect.

226% SpA + 17 x (Level - 1) + 761

Bliss Assistance

Unite Move

112s 100000 Buff

Unlocks at level 8

The user becomes unstoppable and dashes to the designated ally Pokémon to give it an egg, granting that ally a shield and increasing their Attack and Sp. Atk by 20% for 6s. The user also intercepts 50% of the post-mitigation damage received by that ally as unmitigated damage for 6s. While dashing, opposing Pokémon hit are damaged and thrown into the air for 0.8s. When reaching the target ally, nearby opposing Pokémon are damaged again.

94.4% SpA + 25 x (Level - 1) + 1190

240% SpA + 0 x (Level - 1) + 1200

Unite Buffs (6s duration):

30% Movement Speed, 30% CDR, 20% Max HP Shield
